Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.66,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.13,0:00:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.67,0:00:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.78,0:00:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.99,0:00:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.79,0:00:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.07,0:01:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.51,0:01:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.18,0:01:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.52,0:01:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.09,0:01:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要让我下去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠钢弹!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.97,0:01:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，我的沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十八话\N[破坏托尔吉斯]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些技师的来历知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.38,0:02:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们果然是本来曾参予
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.69,0:02:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为OZ开发机动战士的技师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开发托尔吉斯途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.69,0:02:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正确来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在完成了托尔吉斯的设计图后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.16,0:02:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5人就全部失踪，下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是杰克斯特校使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人称原型里欧的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然是20年前设计出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.71,0:02:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在地球仍是最强的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.38,0:02:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最强这个形容词不适当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.62,0:02:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最强的是要让所有士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它当作自己的荣耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他们制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯，不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.86,0:03:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胜过钢弹的最强机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长，我把杰克斯特校带来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地方狭窄对不起，请坐在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特校不需要那种待遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你不自在，对不起，杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你不要介意，特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已准备上军事法庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果你今后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也肯为罗姆斐拉财团出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法庭就不会那么为难你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.28,0:03:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在地上最强的机动战士钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今后也愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.65,0:04:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为打倒钢弹的骑士作战吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人，很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能遵从罗姆斐拉财团的意愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹凭着战争时不须要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个人感情在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和钢弹的战斗已经完结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?那么，杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就为了OZ牺牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.68,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你受审被判有罪会对OZ有害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光荣战死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才会令众多士兵为你哀悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令他们拥有更激昂的斗志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.49,0:04:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团\N的高层当然也会同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闪电伯爵的称号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会成为传说中的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的死有那么大的价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死后就会自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永别了，杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在所有人离去后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,50部艾亚利兹和20部坎沙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会攻击这艘舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对手是想巴结财团的联合余党
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然任务是瞒过财团高层耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放走杰克斯特校你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但把你当作敌人\N我觉得太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，这是身为特列斯的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活下去的考验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我想做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也瞒不过特列斯的心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模拟战开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是MD系统吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于用开发的是旧型里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要从机外输入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在宇宙用MD陶拉斯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就毫无问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性能很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD足以增强兵力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫技师长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，代替士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为主要军力的日子亦不远吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人正攻击这里!他没答话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!刚好作为MD的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫它们攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知死活的敌人间谍吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人里欧有通讯进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.93,0:06:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.93,0:06:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击中止!中止!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想代表血肉之驱的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑战MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想死吗?特列斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD不会像人类般留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果MD是优秀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.91,0:06:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就不须要存在于这世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想在这里\N分出高下，通话完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他疯了吗? 不要紧，攻击特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是命令，他想杀死我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，动手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!我做不到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你停止!技师长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死兹巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停…停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照特列斯特校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要当场把你枪决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了，兹巴洛夫技师长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是驾驶机动战士战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是战争啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们胜利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操纵MD\N和士兵的也是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.64,0:07:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你多一点赞赏和爱惜人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，快点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有你，OZ会容许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无用的人做出无礼的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了!是穿过OZ监视的穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这条航路OZ较少使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我们能俘虏钢弹了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正确来说是钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝着这里来的穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是用来搬运机动战士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.84,0:08:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，拘留那士兵做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹的驾驶员是为了和OZ战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才回来宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有相同的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要和那驾驶员交涉联手抗敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.79,0:08:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以把那驾驶员交给OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.13,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确保我们自身的安全吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和把偷袭当作上策的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通交涉根本不会有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只有和OZ全面战斗一途!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高速机急速接近这里!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.81,0:08:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信是OZ的机动战士陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有20部宇宙里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.51,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能打赢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我应该说过别轻视OZ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ知道这一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.45,0:09:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藏有联合宇宙军的残余中队!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们只是用5部陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就来攻击联合的残余部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别把钢弹的驾驶员交给他们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的机动战士分散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有飞行物体接近后退了的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们发现了\N从地球来的钢弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前来迎击的全是普通型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙战用里欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!把它们设定为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的攻击目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里交给你，我去追穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到是无人开动的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在毫无障碍物的宇宙里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们认为那是有效的武器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不污染自己双手的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这已经是游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发动战争的人类是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在战斗里流的血不会白流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愚蠢的人类看见那些血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少许也好，他们也能反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但沦为游戏的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会成为娱乐的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如用游戏分出胜负就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，谁也不用死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果对手也有那种技术就是游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非没有技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了用自身感觉战争的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们才不给予自动机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们能给予吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你们就能活得久一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不能制造呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.92,0:10:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要做那种事，死掉更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.09,0:10:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然年轻人认为合理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但发动战争并不合理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本来想叫你们制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比你们的托尔吉斯和钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.46,0:10:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有更高性能的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.27,0:10:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死我们吧，我们不会协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不痛苦亦不后悔的战争游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谈判决裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!尼哥尔特尉有联络来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.45,0:11:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?尼哥尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校\N我接收到联合的无线电
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.05,0:11:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想和钢弹的驾驶员联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.42,0:11:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧!把一切毁灭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.67,0:11:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一瞬间消灭了5部吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人机动战士加速前去8时方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么怪物!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经消灭联合的主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即夺取穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夺取?别做无谓的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们根本不需要\N没有钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把通讯系统借给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是卡特尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到宇宙的同伴啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起保护卫星吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在使用希洛的线路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是个优秀的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.98,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有团结5名钢弹驾驶员的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是…卡特尔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.79,0:12:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到宇宙的同伴啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.82,0:13:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起保护卫星吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止毁灭穿梭机!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你原来有可怜部下的心吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好说话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是为OZ制造钢弹吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你们制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以胜过钢弹的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个少年就是钢弹的驾驶员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队长，所有陶拉斯正朝着这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能尽量离开穿梭机作战吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.06,0:13:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中止攻击穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯部队离开穿梭机的航路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?中止攻击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是放走穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在宇宙漂浮是它的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但航路上的垃圾一定要清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥尔，毁灭它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙里欧交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去毁灭穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭机仍然毫无动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我开始打扫航路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭机攻击里欧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.59,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭机还能航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体追击!毁灭它!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我们没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和OZ对抗的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.77,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…那个驾驶员做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.91,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望我的计谋能得到回报就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.99,0:15:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起…保护宇宙吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来接你的直升机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.44,0:15:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.44,0:15:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托尔吉斯的修理如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠你的部下，修理得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,后方4030方向有雷达反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了吗?好准时啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.65,0:15:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这艘舰会被击沉，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.19,0:15:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你尽情战斗，虽然心情很复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，特校，请你一定要赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.53,0:16:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出击了，托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亚利兹50部!坎沙20部!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要证明给他们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们太轻视我的性命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有多少部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有决心!\N但我还不可以死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯!别那么执着!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是不想回应\N无谓的期望吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直至面具碎掉为止啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我不能成为你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永别了，特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太阳系内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.67,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生物能奇蹟地生活繁殖的惑星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在卫星开发上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类凭着丰富的资源和技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到新的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.49,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模拟地球那片母亲大地的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.23,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,制造卫星有什么意义呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说它的主要目的是开发技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.27,0:19:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令地球的人类过得丰裕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类在这些模拟空间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有无理的要求吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的生命\N不会受到大自然威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有比地球高的稳定性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有停顿的发展\N好像答应了人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.32,0:19:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让其永远生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙有容许由零开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而陶醉的时代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但卫星…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类能够忘记地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的技术开发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为地球带来了什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球最想要的技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破坏是人类不能抛弃的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.62,0:20:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在卫星正不断拥有军事技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们不能忘记地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的美丽是伟大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有强大力量名为人类的动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也想管理一个惑星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在惑星之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生物的生存是刹那间的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是短暂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类能想到的始终…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.24,0:20:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫无改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.28,0:20:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类飞出宇宙的岁月是白费的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在现实面前，理想只是梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虚假的生活空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虚假的和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙只是孕育更多战争的温床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争会夺去很多生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.69,0:21:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然人类从未\N忘记过战争的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们绝对不想停止战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流下的血和泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是仪式的装饰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时代里只有用战争讲述的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为和平而战这等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经过修饰的漂亮话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.05,0:21:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是过去多次被高呼的名句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.72,0:21:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星为了和平而拥有军备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球毫无分别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他们能加入成为同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉着流很多血，活下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此为止吧，迪欧‧麦斯威尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止那题目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.47,0:21:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强迫大家不安不大好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,转校后和大家这样打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教师我认为有点问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.94,0:21:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，迪欧同学\N你坐在最后一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，人类为何要战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗里或许有存在的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.02,0:22:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗的人类有充实感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.29,0:22:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，战斗的人类不会腐败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.40,0:22:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.72,0:22:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血来潮的找人出来\N只因为天气好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.72,0:22:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我一直等不到人\N你以为你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.72,0:22:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑过来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.22,0:22:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那个惹人厌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.72,0:23:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因为心理有爱意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.22,0:23:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是让人挂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.72,0:23:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N我不该说出强人所难的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.72,0:23:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.41,0:23:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落卫星的钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.08,0:23:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有赞美也没有奖赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.02,0:23:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们只有消灭OZ的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.36,0:23:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神钢弹和陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙空间战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.23,0:23:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，迪欧战败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.99,0:23:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为OZ的俘虏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛为了保守秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.47,0:23:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去杀死迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新机动战记-钢弹W，第十九话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.67,0:23:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强袭巴尔吉

